Ive always said 97% of humans dont change. Yeah, sure they change a little bit over time, but the core of who they are remains the same. People are who they are. Its all they know.

Anuway, as i sit here and watch this interview with mike...I cant help but noticr the 180° he has done with not only his demeanor, but the 180° he has done with his life.

I used to wonder if Mike would ever find his peace....

Now im wondering if I'll ever find mine.
